content: I have used this on several devices incuding fire tablets. And LG k92 5G with not much issues. Sometimes it fails to initiate track scan. I do love the throttle contoll in this vs the Fast and Furious App. But i want the 2.6..... To support MXT and Ice Charger.

Sad to say it did not work on my OnePlus. The app is no longer playable on IOS. I've supported both platforms and my user experience is not good. The app continually crashes when I attempt to start a race. I had to use the old anki version for it to work.
Does not save your progress on tornament
I can't use it on my tablet that is why i gave it 1 star but my other divices 5 stars much better then the free one PS thanks DDL

Tournament mode has never worked. Cars fail to stay connected. Ordered tires from DLL. NO RESPONSE. Basically I have yet to have a positive experience or reassurance that the app or any other issues will ever be addressed in a professional manner.
Please fix this app. None of our progress is saving. Just fix it.
Chapters don't save.
Needs more content. Once tournament is completed, there is nothing to do.
i was excited for this but theres alot of problems in the app. 1st whenever you scan the app closes 2nd i lose most of my weapons i thought it was gonna be great but it sucks.

I wanted this to work so bad...but more of the same disappointment we had when Anki was running the show. The cars disconnect mid race if they connect at all. History is not saved in the single player part of the game making you start over everytime. We haven't been able to even play one full race. I guess it goes back on the shelf where it has been for over a year. I hate that I wasted $3 on this product when I said I was done spending money on it so long ago.

Single player works fine, but keep getting player disconnect message when trying to play multiplayer, both have updated app and using android phone and tablet, same happens when using ipad - please fix for next update
...waiting for app to work properly.. update Sept 2020 app works better.. can't save progress..
The fast and furious cars can not be selected this needs to be addressed. Some nice new additions to this app great racing game

This is a very good game. I'm new to overdrive and it is awesome. It works great with my phone, which is considered a dinosaur in phone years. The only problem I have is the throttle slider lags a bit sometimes, but it's only for a few seconds and doesn't hamper the performance. Whatever problems you guys are having is most likely with your phone and not the app itself. GREAT game.
Cool enough

Big fan of the relaunch. I'd never played the 2.6 version before and was skeptical of the decision to put resources into launching the old version. This is a much cleaner game. Works well on multiple Android devices. There is a bug trying to play without doing the training first, but otherwise üëç
missing compatability with all cars, for some reason campain refreshing; all medals which I had as well have been lost for no reason.
Pay money ? No

Update. So I thought I'd try the app again, it's now asking me to pay for the app once more. I've Allready purchased it, why should I have to purchase again to use it. Not a great start, only 1 of my cars is reconised, so I restart the app, and no cars reconised.
Will this app support the fast and furious edition?
Please fix it we want this to work, cars won't connect, can't open garage
Having a lot of fun!!! Can't wait to see how it gets better!!
The cars don't connect to the app please update üèéüéÆ
Bought to support the development, I hope it can be made better

I have purchased every overdrive car and super truck plus fast and the furious edition cars. It doesn't recognize my cars. I paid for a better app or so I thought and I cant even use my vehicles. the app is very unstable. So I'm reduced to using the old app and just dealing with those bad issues. DIGITAL DREAM LABS ....PLEASE FIX THESE ISSUES AND BE BETTER THAN ANKI ABOUT TAKING CARE OF YOUR CUSTOMERS OR YOUR ACQUISITION OF THESE AWESOME PRODUCTS WAS USELESS AND ALL FOR NOTHING. PLEASE HELP!!
Theres are lots of glitches and the memory for the tournament isn't saving, but very cool üòé

I missed this version of overdrive, but why I had to pay for this made no sense to me, but I did it nonetheless. Edit- So the story has a progression bug, if you head to the home page none of your progress will save and you'll need to restart

Does not work at moment. When it says put cars on charger it stops working. Cant move on from there. Will not recognise cars. Expected a few blips but to not work at all is poor. Tried different brands of tablet incase that caused the problem
Does not recognise cars after initial start up. Real shame !!!!
Keeps crushing when the game starts
Terrible app. Opened the very first time but since then fails to open every time.

Currently the game is unplayable. the first time I got the app I didn't have the track set up so I opened it and logged it and left it for a few days. I came back to it and it didn't want to connect to any of the cars or the truck I have. I then reinstalled it rhen the app detected everything perfectly, I got completed the truck tutorial and went on to tournament mode, I picked my car and the bot did too. The app then crashed and I tried the same thing again and it wouldn't detect any cars again

I could play once, then I get an error and even after restarting, wiping the offline data,... I get this error and I can't log in anymore: Sentry sent back: {"id":"long id"} And I have the same error (not sure if the id is different) on my iPad.
Doesn't support the fast and furious cars

I don't really know where to start so here's a list. 1) The cars have issues connecting and after you finish the tutorial your lucky if your cars connect at all. 2) When you play the tournament the moment you stop continuing (such as if you go to the garage or want to stop) the tournament reverts back to you not completing a single race. 3) Multiplayer doesn't connect even when our family is connected to our house's wifi. The app makes it impossible to do anything single or multiplayer.
App freeze on login
Great start but there are some issues which they pledge to fix. Thanks for keeping Overdrive alive!

I missed this so much and I'm glad it's back to form. But it has some bugs like not letting me log in because it freezes when I sign in. Also, not being able to launch the app a 2nd time. It freezes on the loading screen on my Samsung Galaxy A8. Customising and upgrading cars doesn't work either. I hope you can fix this because I really want to play again
Awesome job so far by DDL to revive the Overdrive line. Can't wait to see their future updates.

I was very excited for this version. Digital dream seemed to have great ideas for revamping overdrive. I paid the money for this as I believe in what they are trying to do. Unfortunately on my samsung galaxy s8 this game freezes and will not recognize any of my cars or super trucks. It also does not seem to have the fast and furious cars as an option to use. I am very disappointed in it's current state. I hope they can fix this soon.

It is, as has been said, a work in progress. But I'm so pleased DDL are bringing this back to life. The bugs will get ironed out and we're promised lots of new features later, including AR ! Can't wait.
Fun but not quite there yet. Thankyou Digital Game Labs for bringing back Anki.. I am cautiously optimistic for the future.
Great to have Digital Dream Labs here to bring back support for this after Anki went bankrupt. They could've done nothing, but they did! Looking forward to upcoming updates and features!
Super cool , better than the old app but the garage is super glitchy.also can you add a button to reset the shop?
Big thanks for reviving the platform. Works well for an initial release and the gameplay is much better than the Anki 3.4 version. Very much looking forward to future updates
so cool game I can spend hours playing with my kids love this app thank you so much for your hard work
Unfortunately it did not work, seems to show my two cars but we can't select them. Tried on three different phones. Looking forward for future fix.

Ok hoping this will change to 5Star soon. DDL are resurrecting overdrive after the collapse of Anki. They need time to get it right, but for a start, am very happy to have this app updated and working on my devices
Was workin fine, now cars wont connect, cant even to select a car, they are all greyed out, have rebooted pone, turned off the cars, still cant play. Vey dissapointed.
Installed on a Google Pixel 2, just locked it after saying no to access to photos and files. Awful relaunch, and why does it need access anyway?
It's a work in progress, but the gameplay of the original on a newer device. Thank you.

Please stop complaining about the cost of this game. The $3 for this game is a small price to pay to have a new company take over the reigns from Anki and continue to support this great game. I'm looking forward to future builds with expanded futures. Thanks Digital Dream Labs.
I glad they got this back
On a Samsung s9+ this app is currently more broken than the old anki version. Try to modify cars and garage doesn't open then no other buttons work, force quit, try again, still doesn't work.
Thank you for listening to your customer base. There's plenty of room to grow, looking forward to seeing what you can do.
